{
  "name": "15 — Lead Intake Avanzado (form /empezar → email segmentado → nurture)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "lead-intake",
        "responseMode": "onReceived",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "wf15-webhook",
      "name": "Webhook: lead-intake",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [250, 300],
      "webhookId": "lead-intake"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Normalizar y enriquecer los datos del lead\nconst body = $input.first().json.body || $input.first().json;\n\nconst problemLabels = {\n  ventas:      'automatización de ventas',\n  soporte:     'soporte al cliente',\n  marketing:   'marketing con IA',\n  ecommerce:   'e-commerce',\n  leads:       'captación de leads',\n  operaciones: 'automatización de operaciones'\n};\n\nconst problemSubjects = {\n  ventas:      'Cerrá más ventas sin contratar más vendedores',\n  soporte:     'Respondé al 100% de las consultas sin ampliar equipo',\n  marketing:   'Creá contenido y captá leads en piloto automático',\n  ecommerce:   'Automatizá tu e-commerce y convertí más visitantes',\n  leads:       'Llenate de leads calificados sin esfuerzo manual',\n  operaciones: 'Liberá horas de trabajo eliminando tareas repetitivas'\n};\n\nconst agentSuggestions = {\n  ventas:      'Sales AI Closer',\n  soporte:     'AI Support Agent',\n  marketing:   'Marketing AI Agent',\n  ecommerce:   'E-Commerce Agent',\n  leads:       'AI Lead Engine',\n  operaciones: 'Appointment Setting Agent'\n};\n\nconst problem = body.problem_area || 'ventas';\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    lead_id:        body.lead_id,\n    name:           body.name,\n    email:          body.email,\n    whatsapp:       body.whatsapp,\n    company:        body.company,\n    industry:       body.industry,\n    problem_area:   problem,\n    problem_label:  problemLabels[problem] || problem,\n    email_subject:  problemSubjects[problem] || 'Automatizá tu negocio con IA',\n    agent_suggested: agentSuggestions[problem] || 'Sales AI Closer',\n    company_size:   body.company_size,\n    budget_range:   body.budget_range,\n    channel_origin: body.channel_origin,\n    wants_call:     body.wants_call,\n    first_name:     (body.name || '').split(' ')[0]\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "id": "wf15-normalize",
      "name": "Normalizar datos del lead",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [480, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "append",
        "documentId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "1ypxnhwu0KYPDCsNGS5EyZ54F0c2TJLUQrdDgvYTMa98",
          "mode": "id"
        },
        "sheetName": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "Leads Master",
          "mode": "name"
        },
        "columns": {
          "mappingMode": "defineBelow",
          "value": {
            "Fecha":          "={{ $now.format('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') }}",
            "Lead_ID":        "={{ $json.lead_id }}",
            "Nombre":         "={{ $json.name }}",
            "Email":          "={{ $json.email }}",
            "WhatsApp":       "={{ $json.whatsapp }}",
            "Empresa":        "={{ $json.company }}",
            "Industria":      "={{ $json.industry }}",
            "Problema":       "={{ $json.problem_area }}",
            "Tamaño_empresa": "={{ $json.company_size }}",
            "Presupuesto":    "={{ $json.budget_range }}",
            "Canal_origen":   "={{ $json.channel_origin }}",
            "Quiere_llamada": "={{ $json.wants_call }}",
            "Agente_sugerido": "={{ $json.agent_suggested }}",
            "Estado":         "nuevo"
          }
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "wf15-sheets",
      "name": "Sheets: agregar a Leads Master",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets",
      "typeVersion": 4,
      "position": [720, 300],
      "credentials": {
        "googleSheetsOAuth2Api": {
          "id": "fcrCF63uNbwzoCEy",
          "name": "Google Sheets OAuth2"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Construir email de bienvenida segmentado por problema\nconst d = $input.first().json;\n\nconst agentUrl = `https://tuagentestore.com/agents/${d.agent_suggested.toLowerCase().replace(/\\s+/g,'-').replace(/[^a-z0-9-]/g,'')}`;\nconst empezarUrl = `https://tuagentestore.com/empezar?problema=${d.problem_area}`;\n\nconst body = `\n<div style=\"font-family:Inter,system-ui,sans-serif;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;background:#0a0f1e;color:#e2e8f0;padding:40px 32px;border-radius:16px\">\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom:32px\">\n    <span style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3b82f6,#6366f1);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;font-weight:800;font-size:20px\">TuAgenteStore</span>\n  </div>\n  <h1 style=\"font-size:24px;font-weight:800;color:#f1f5f9;margin-bottom:12px\">¡Hola ${d.first_name}! 👋</h1>\n  <p style=\"color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:24px\">Recibimos tu consulta sobre <strong style=\"color:#f1f5f9\">${d.problem_label}</strong>. Nos ponemos en contacto en las próximas 2 horas.</p>\n  \n  <div style=\"background:#1e293b;border:1px solid #334155;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:28px\">\n    <p style=\"color:#94a3b8;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:8px\">Agente sugerido para tu caso:</p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight:700;font-size:18px;color:#f1f5f9;margin-bottom:4px\">${d.agent_suggested}</p>\n    <a href=\"${agentUrl}\" style=\"color:#60a5fa;font-size:14px;text-decoration:none\">Ver este agente →</a>\n  </div>\n\n  <p style=\"color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:28px\">Mientras tanto, podés explorar todos los agentes disponibles y ver demos en vivo de cada uno.</p>\n\n  <a href=\"https://tuagentestore.com/agents\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3b82f6,#6366f1);color:#fff;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:12px;font-weight:600;font-size:16px\">Ver todos los agentes →</a>\n\n  <hr style=\"border:none;border-top:1px solid #1e293b;margin:36px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#475569;font-size:13px\">TuAgenteStore · Buenos Aires, Argentina · <a href=\"https://tuagentestore.com\" style=\"color:#475569\">tuagentestore.com</a></p>\n</div>\n`;\n\nreturn [{ json: { ...d, email_body: body } }];"
      },
      "id": "wf15-build-email",
      "name": "Construir email bienvenida",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [960, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "sendTo":  "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "={{ $json.email_subject }} — TuAgenteStore",
        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "={{ $json.email_body }}",
        "options": {
          "ccList": "admin@tuagentestore.com"
        }
      },
      "id": "wf15-gmail-welcome",
      "name": "Gmail: email bienvenida segmentado",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.gmail",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1200, 300],
      "credentials": {
        "gmailOAuth2": {
          "id": "EzOwUZC8g74ixDQC",
          "name": "Gmail OAuth2"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "amount": 48,
        "unit": "hours"
      },
      "id": "wf15-wait-48h",
      "name": "Esperar 48 horas",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.wait",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1440, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "={{ $env.NEXT_APP_URL || 'https://tuagentestore.com' }}/api/admin/reservations",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "name": "x-webhook-secret", "value": "={{ $env.WEBHOOK_SECRET_INTERNAL }}" }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "wf15-check-conversion",
      "name": "Check: ¿convirtió?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4,
      "position": [1680, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": { "caseSensitive": false },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "leftValue":  "={{ $json.reservations?.find(r => r.user_email === $('wf15-normalize').first().json.email && r.status !== 'new') }}",
              "rightValue": "",
              "operator": { "type": "object", "operation": "notEmpty" }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "wf15-if-converted",
      "name": "IF: ¿ya avanzó en el pipeline?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1920, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const d = $('wf15-normalize').first().json;\n\nconst body = `\n<div style=\"font-family:Inter,system-ui,sans-serif;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;background:#0a0f1e;color:#e2e8f0;padding:40px 32px;border-radius:16px\">\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom:32px\">\n    <span style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3b82f6,#6366f1);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;font-weight:800;font-size:20px\">TuAgenteStore</span>\n  </div>\n  <h1 style=\"font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#f1f5f9;margin-bottom:12px\">Hola ${d.first_name}, ¿pudiste revisar el agente?</h1>\n  <p style=\"color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:24px\">Hace 48 horas nos dejaste tu consulta sobre <strong style=\"color:#f1f5f9\">${d.problem_label}</strong>. ¿Tuviste la oportunidad de ver la demo?</p>\n  \n  <div style=\"background:#1e293b;border:1px solid #334155;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:28px\">\n    <p style=\"color:#94a3b8;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:4px\">El agente que te sugerimos:</p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight:700;font-size:18px;color:#f1f5f9\">${d.agent_suggested}</p>\n    <p style=\"color:#94a3b8;font-size:14px;margin-top:8px\">Miles de empresas ya lo usan para ${d.problem_label}.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <p style=\"color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:28px\">Si tenés dudas o querés hablar con un especialista, respondé este email o agendá una llamada de 30 minutos:</p>\n\n  <a href=\"https://tuagentestore.com/empezar?problema=${d.problem_area}\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3b82f6,#6366f1);color:#fff;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:12px;font-weight:600;font-size:16px\">Agendar llamada gratuita →</a>\n\n  <hr style=\"border:none;border-top:1px solid #1e293b;margin:36px 0\">\n  <p style=\"color:#475569;font-size:12px\">Si no querés recibir más emails, respondé con \"cancelar\". · TuAgenteStore</p>\n</div>\n`;\n\nreturn [{ json: { ...d, reminder_body: body } }];"
      },
